Class TwoWayAltAutomaton

java.lang.Object
org.svvrl.goal.core.AbstractEditable
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.Automaton
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.alt.AbstractAltAutomaton
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.alt.twoway.TwoWayAltAutomaton
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.EventListener, Editable
public class TwoWayAltAutomaton
extends AbstractAltAutomaton
A TwoWayAltAutomaton is an alternating automaton with two directions on transitions.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
